1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,036
<i>Previously on Desperate Housewives...</i>

2
00:00:02,037 --> 00:00:04,709
<i>While Ian's wife Jane
was in a coma...</i>

3
00:00:04,710 --> 00:00:05,455
Do we have a deal?

4
00:00:05,456 --> 00:00:06,829
<i>Susan got an ultimatum.</i>

5
00:00:06,830 --> 00:00:10,017
He's not crazy about me
spending time with my ex.

6
00:00:11,251 --> 00:00:12,657
Mike's new hero...

7
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:14,292
Owe you one.

8
00:00:14,293 --> 00:00:17,371
After those mutts knocked you around
the other day, your boy paid 'em off.

9
00:00:17,372 --> 00:00:19,048
...had a secret agenda

10
00:00:19,293 --> 00:00:20,274
Gabrielle.

11
00:00:20,307 --> 00:00:22,507
<i>Gabrielle learned the identity...</i>

12
00:00:22,508 --> 00:00:24,671
I’m rich now. I can give you
anything you want.

13
00:00:24,672 --> 00:00:26,404
<i>...of her secret admirer.</i>

14
00:00:26,405 --> 00:00:27,516
Tell me everything.

15
00:00:27,517 --> 00:00:32,137
<i>and Orson's mother shared some
family secrets that Bree...</o></i>

16
00:00:33,510 --> 00:00:35,339
<i>...would later discover.</i>

17
00:00:38,624 --> 00:00:43,599
<i>If there was one thing Orson Hodge
understood, it was teeth.</i>

18
00:00:45,765 --> 00:00:48,862
<i>that's why people stopped him
at barbecues...</i>

19
00:00:50,521 --> 00:00:52,472
<i>during cocktail parties...</i>

20
00:00:54,565 --> 00:00:57,492
<i>and in the occasional men's room.</i>

21
00:00:59,974 --> 00:01:02,267
<i>Yes, when it came to teeth,</i>

22
00:01:02,268 --> 00:01:06,584
<i>people expected Dr. Hodge
to have all the answers.</i>

23
00:01:06,585 --> 00:01:10,970
<i>sadly for Orson,
this was not always the case.</i>

24
00:01:14,016 --> 00:01:15,918
Well, it does look  a little fishy.

25
00:01:15,919 --> 00:01:16,918
Fishy?

26
00:01:17,113 --> 00:01:18,967
It couldn't be more obvious.

27
00:01:19,181 --> 00:01:21,035
Alma killed Monique.

28
00:01:21,036 --> 00:01:22,458
That's why she disappeared.

29
00:01:22,459 --> 00:01:25,580
And I bet she pulled the teeth so people
would suspect her dentist husband.

30
00:01:25,581 --> 00:01:26,824
Well, why would she keep them?

31
00:01:26,825 --> 00:01:29,812
Who knows ? She's probably gonna sneak
in and plant them in our house.

32
00:01:29,813 --> 00:01:32,788
Well, we've saved her the trouble,
haven't we? Is it a full set?

33
00:01:33,808 --> 00:01:37,223
- Orson! Not on the duvet!
- Oh, it's okay. They won't stain.

34
00:01:37,224 --> 00:01:39,427
I don't care! I am not sleeping
in a bed

35
00:01:39,428 --> 00:01:41,613
that had your dead
mistress' teeth in it!

36
00:01:42,227 --> 00:01:44,691
Let's just take them to the police.

37
00:01:44,692 --> 00:01:48,418
And say what? We can't prove
these came from Alma's.

38
00:01:48,419 --> 00:01:51,536
She'll deny ever having seen. And don't
forget, I’m the one they suspect.

39
00:01:51,537 --> 00:01:53,097
Well, we have to do something.

40
00:01:53,098 --> 00:01:56,292
I agree, but not until we put
this back in her house.

41
00:01:57,524 --> 00:01:58,861
And then we'll call the police.

42
00:01:58,862 --> 00:02:01,446
Trust me, she'll never get away with it.

43
00:02:14,638 --> 00:02:15,663
Hello.

44
00:02:16,858 --> 00:02:18,590
You've been very naughty, haven't you?

45
00:02:18,829 --> 00:02:22,561
Orson? Is that you?

46
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:25,915
I know what you and Alma are
up to, and it's gonna stop.

47
00:02:25,916 --> 00:02:29,519
<i>Yes, Orson was an expert on teeth.</i>

48
00:02:29,862 --> 00:02:33,057
I have no idea what
you're talking about.

49
00:02:33,833 --> 00:02:35,760
Oh, I think you do.

50
00:02:36,413 --> 00:02:40,853
<i>That's how he could tell when
people were lying through them.</i>

